These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, pomegranate, apricot, pepper
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, pop, r&b, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: british, thai, german, japanese
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, snake, bird
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 2. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
 3. the british is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the german is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 7. the thai is the person eating apricot##1
 8. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the bird and the fan of punk##2
10. the person eating peach is the owner of the bird##1
11. the fan of r&b is the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | apricot  | peach    | pepper    | pomegranate   |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | hip-hop   | r&b       | punk    |
| Nationality   | thai | british | japanese    | german |
| Pet           | dog | bird       | mouse | snake     |

