.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pomegranate, peach, cranberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, skydiving, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, polish, nigerian, german
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, badminton, parkour
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
 2. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is the egyptian##1
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 6. the egyptian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 8. the german is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 9. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating peach is in an odd position##4
11. the nigerian is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry  | pomegranate    | peach     | cranberry       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | singing | puzzles   | reading |
| Nationality   | nigerian | egyptian   | polish   | german    |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour  | cricket | ice-hockey   |

