.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, musician, freelancer, mechanic
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, american, colombian, french
4 different pets are kept: pony, rat, hamster, frog
 1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 2. the american is the freelancer##1
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 4. the nurse is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the person drinking water is the mechanic##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the owner of the pony is the french##1
 8. the mechanic is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the australian##1
10. the owner of the pony is the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea | soy-milk   | iced-tea    | water      |
| Job           | freelancer | nurse | musician | mechanic     |
| Nationality   | american      | french   | australian   | colombian |
| Pet           | frog         | pony       | hamster  | rat       |

