.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, almond-milk, coffee
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, raspberry, artichoke, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, skydiving, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, swimming, volleyball
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating strawberry##1
12. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee       | almond-milk   | mirinda   | juice   |
| Food       | raspberry        | strawberry | cabbage    | artichoke       |
| Hobby      | cooking | dancing    | skydiving  | board-games |
| Sport      | weightlifting  | swimming  | climbing | volleyball    |

