.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, peas, lime, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, chess, drawing, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, project-manager, coach, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing, biathlon, climbing
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person eating pepper##2
 3. the coach is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the project-manager is the person eating peach##1
 5. the freelancer is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating peas is the freelancer##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is the project-manager##1
 9. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
10. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | lime    | pepper      | peach          | peas    |
| Hobby   | chess | card-games       | drawing | video-games |
| Job     | social-worker     | coach      | project-manager     | freelancer |
| Sport   | rowing   | climbing | biathlon        | lacrosse   |

