.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, watermelon, onion, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, funk, disco, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, russian, italian
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of indie is between the russian and the fan of funk##2
 7. the fan of disco is the person eating onion##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating onion##1
 9. the dutch is on the far right##1
10. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk  | almond-milk    | coffee       | hot-chocolate       |
| Food          | radish    | onion | watermelon | grapefruit     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | disco        | indie    | funk   |
| Nationality   | argentine  | russian      | italian    | dutch |

