 4. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the colombian##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
