 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the russian and the person watching romance movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

