The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, hip-hop, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, badminton, surfing, rugby
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of reggae is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person eating lettuce is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | lettuce     | apricot      | artichoke  | pomegranate        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | action | adventure | mystery      |
