 3. the coach is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the lawyer is on the left of the coach##1
10. the accountant is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
