.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, sprite, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, gardening, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, romance, zombie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, surfing, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite       | coffee | iced-tea        | almond-milk        |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | gardening       | dancing | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | animation        | scientific    | romance      |
| Sport         | rowing     | surfing    | rugby | baseball   |

