.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, gospel, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, brazilian, egyptian, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, weightlifting, sailing, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, ship, motorbike, scooter
 1. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is between the turkish and the dutch##2
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the fan of funk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 8. the dutch is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
10. the turkish is in an even position##4
11. the turkish is on the far right##1
12. the fan of classical is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | classical | trance     | gospel        |
| Nationality   | egyptian | dutch  | brazilian     | turkish |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | climbing | sailing      | soccer |
| Transport     | scooter | ship     | motorbike | boat       |

 